# Input Fields

**Figma:** [Input / TextField](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10423&p=f&m=dev)

Structure, states, variants, and token mappings below are derived from Figma node 128:10423.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Surface | `--bg-base-default` |
| Border default | `--border-base-default` |
| Border focus | `--border-brand-default` |
| Border error | `--border-danger-default` |
| Label | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Value text | `--text-base-default` |
| Placeholder | `--text-disabled-default` |
| Helper default | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Helper error | `--text-danger-default` |
| Leading/trailing icons | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Disabled bg | `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Disabled text | `--text-disabled-default` |

---

## Structure

- **Label:** Above input; `--text-base-secondary`; Space/100 gap.
- **Input:** Border radius Radius/100 (4px).
- **Helper text:** Below input; Space/100 gap.
- **Layout:** Vertical stack; label → input → helper.

---

## States

| State | Border | Background | Text |
|-------|-------|------------|------|
| Default | `--border-base-default` | `--bg-base-default` | `--text-base-default` |
| Filled | Same | Same | Same |
| Focused | `--border-brand-default` 2px | Same | Same |
| Error | `--border-danger-default` | Same | Helper: `--text-danger-default` |
| Disabled | Lighter/dashed | `--bg-base-tertiary` | `--text-disabled-default` |
| Read-only | Same as default | Same | Non-interactive; distinct from disabled |

---

## Sizes

| Size | Height | Padding |
|------|--------|---------|
| Small | ~32px | Space/200 |
| Medium | ~40px | Space/200–300 |
| Large | ~48px | Space/300–400 |

---

## Types and variants (from Figma)

- **Text:** Single-line; optional leading (search) or trailing (eye, clear X) icon.
- **Password:** Masked; trailing eye icon to toggle visibility.
- **SearchBar:** Leading search icon; compact; optional clear.
- **TextArea:** Multi-line; min height ~80px; vertically expandable.
- **Number:** Spinner (up/down); optional min/max/step.
- **Date picker:** Calendar icon; placeholder "dd-mm-yyyy".
- **Dropdown:** Chevron right; selected value or placeholder.
- **Multi-select:** Tag-like selected items with close icons.
- **With units:** Predefined units (% or currency) adjacent.
- **Character counter:** "0/100" below; `--text-base-secondary`.

---

## Props (from Figma)

- **Type:** Text, Number, Password, Email, Search, Tel, URL, Date, Time, DateTime-local, Month, Week, Color.
- **Icon:** Left, Right, None.
- **Clearable:** Yes/No.
- **Optional:** Yes/No (label indicator).
- **Read-only:** Yes/No.

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Focus: `focus:border-[var(--border-brand-default)] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[var(--border-brand-default)]`.
- Error: `border-[var(--border-danger-default)]`; helper `text-[var(--text-danger-default)]`.
- Leading/trailing icons: padding Space/200–300.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10423.
